719725f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - Fairview Avenue
719725f-a.text:
Broadwav (street level not seen, being betNeen buildings
and hillock) at Fairwuiew Avenue, as viewed from Wadsworth Terrace
and across intervening roof tops. Shown atop the bluff are: the
castlelike structure of Dr. Chas V. Paterno; the studio of Geo.
Barnard Grey; and the ransion and estate of C.N.G. Billings. The
latter is today apart of Fort Tryon Park.
9ctober 26, 1927.
Views 1 and 2
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIO5S.
